         <abstract id="aspace_cb7f27231997fcb3979aadafe96e3d03">Scrapbooks, record books, and memorabilia chiefly relating to the educational and library activities at the Relocation Center. Nine scrapbooks made and bound by the students cover topics of academic study as well as their memoirs describing their feelings on being relocated. A printed yearbook is also included.</abstract>
